node.title: Person killed in Auckland house fire
node.content: ["A person has died in a house fire in the Auckland suburb of Avondale.", "Emergency services were called to the blaze on Blockhouse Bay Rd just after midnight on Wednesday.", "A police statement said surrounding residents were evacuated as a precaution.", "Sadly, a person was found dead at the scene, the statement said.", "Fire investigators are working with the police to determine the cause of the blaze."]
